stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> generating: worker claimed
  generating --> postprocess: mesh/texture complete
  postprocess --> ready: validate + publish
  generating --> failed: timeout/error
  postprocess --> failed: validation error
  failed --> generating: retry (attempt < max)
  failed --> ready: fallback policy success
  failed --> [*]: keep_placeholder
  ready --> [*]
